description: HttpM: Table storing HTTP Measurement data for specific cells in a given area, including timestamps, cell identifiers, and versioning information.  `dateTime`: Timestamp of the measurement; `Area_Name`: Geographic area of the cell; `CellId`: Unique identifier of the cell; `Id2`: Redundant cell identifier; `Id3`: Unknown identifier; `Id4`: Unknown identifier; `vsDataType`: Data type identifier; `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format; `HttpM.httpMId`: Unique ID for the HTTP measurement record.
